  <Placemark>
    <name>La Quinta de las Piedras (Miguel Menchaca House)</name>
    <description><![CDATA[<b>Address:</b> 19801 Scenic Loop Rd., Helotes<br/><br/><b>Marker Text:</b> Home of Miguel Menchaca, descendant of prominent Canary Islanders who came to texas 1731. Stone villa built in 1850's. In its thick rock walls are "gun-slits" for observation, defense. Spring under house supplied water in times of siege. Recorded Texas Historic Landmark, 1965.]]></description>
